<section id="privacy-notice">
  <center><h3>Privacy Notice</h3></center>
  <p>For research purposes, this site uses Google Analytics to collect
    aggregate information about, e.g., how often the site is used and what 
    links are followed from it. We do not collect personally identifiable 
    information, but if you have a Gmail account or have ever Googled 
    yourself from your own computer, then, despite their assurances to the 
    contrary, <b>Google does collect such information.</b> We recommend that you use <a href="http://adblockplus.org/">AdBlock Plus</a>, <a href="http://ghostery.com/">Ghostery</a>, <a href="http://noscript.org/">NoScript</a>, and/or <a href="http://privoxy.org/">Privoxy</a>
    to protect your browsing privacy. The first two are really easy to 
    install and use; the last two take a bit more effort to whitelist sites 
    you trust. (You might also consider the tracking-free <a href="http://duckduckgo.com/">DuckDuckGo</a> search engine.)</p>
  <p>See our complete privacy policy <a href="http://snap.berkeley.edu/privacy.html">here</a>.</p>
